messages.message: I'm not very familiar with License service (everything I know about it, I learned tonight), but I think it makes sense to unit test LicenseMgr.Init() to make sure that the proper actions are being taken upon initialization of License Service. I attempted to write such a unit test but didn't quite get it to a working state. Someone more familiar with License Service might want to take on the task!
Thanks Naveen! I'll follow up and add a unit test for this. Sorry for the spin everyone.
